				<p>Before optimizing, you need to understand your current resource usage:</p>

				<h3>Key Metrics to Track</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Compute Utilization:</strong> CPU/GPU usage percentages</li>
					<li><strong>Memory Usage:</strong> RAM consumption and memory leaks</li>
					<li><strong>Inference Latency:</strong> Time to process requests</li>
					<li><strong>Throughput:</strong> Requests processed per second</li>
					<li><strong>Cost per Request:</strong> Total cost divided by number of requests</li>
				</ul>

