				<h3>Model Compression Techniques</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Quantization:</strong> Reduce precision from 32-bit to 8-bit or 16-bit</li>
					<li><strong>Pruning:</strong> Remove unnecessary weights and connections</li>
					<li><strong>Knowledge Distillation:</strong> Train smaller models to mimic larger ones</li>
					<li><strong>Model Architecture Search:</strong> Find optimal architectures automatically</li>
				</ul>

